# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:14
translate spanish jezp1_4c67be19:

    # det "Craziest case? Honestly this whole meth thing is the craziest, by far, but you know all about that."
    det "¿El caso más loco? Sinceramente, todo este asunto de la metanfetamina es, con diferencia, el más loco, pero eso ya lo sabes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:15
translate spanish jezp1_f9ba8ba2:

    # pc "Okay, what's second?"
    pc "Vale, ¿y el segundo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:17
translate spanish jezp1_d2ba3c59:

    # det "Well second would probably be this quantum physicist who went missing..."
    det "Bueno, el segundo probablemente sería el de ese físico cuántico que desapareció..."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:19
translate spanish jezp1_7917e354:

    # det "... and the only clues we've found are some notes about meth and stolen diamonds."
    det "... y las únicas pistas que hemos encontrado son unas notas sobre metanfetamina y diamantes robados."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:20
translate spanish jezp1_9f944501:

    # pc "I think I've heard that one too."
    pc "Creo que también he oído hablar de ese."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:22
translate spanish jezp1_fdb1b83e:

    # det "There's not a lot of crazy stories that happen in Skyhill. It's a pretty quiet place, overall."
    det "No hay muchas historias locas que pasen en Skyhill. Es un lugar bastante tranquilo, en general."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:24
translate spanish jezp1_65e698d3:

    # det "Oh, wait! I know one."
    det "¡Oh, espera! Yo conozco una."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:25
translate spanish jezp1_e06ef57f:

    # pc "Tell me!"
    pc "¡Cuéntamela!"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:27
translate spanish jezp1_bf50abb1:

    # det "So, a few years ago, there was a couple that lived in the apartments over on Birch Street."
    det "Bueno, hace unos años, había una pareja que vivía en los apartamentos de Birch Street."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:28
translate spanish jezp1_97ea4bf4:

    # det "A burglar broke in while they were out shopping. They came back and found the place ransacked."
    det "Un ladrón entró mientras estaban fuera de compras. Volvieron y encontraron la casa revuelta."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:29
translate spanish jezp1_61dd60a4:

    # det "Jewelry stolen, some small electronics, cash, all that."
    det "Les habían robado joyas, algunos aparatos electrónicos pequeños, dinero en efectivo, todo eso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:31
translate spanish jezp1_c93c92fc:

    # det "Well after we started looking through things, the guy notices a backpack that doesn't belong to them."
    det "Bueno, cuando empezamos a revisar las cosas, el chico se fijó en una mochila que no era de ellos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:32
translate spanish jezp1_c09a7dec:

    # det "We check it out and find some of the couple's valuables inside..."
    det "La revisamos y encontramos algunos de los objetos de valor de la pareja dentro..."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:34
translate spanish jezp1_fc50a5c2:

    # det "... along with some homework with the student's name on it. And even better, his college ID."
    det "... junto con unos deberes con el nombre del estudiante. Y aún mejor, su carné universitario."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:35
translate spanish jezp1_5b56cc12:

    # pc "Ha! So the burglar forgot his bookbag?"
    pc "¡Ja! ¿Así que el ladrón se olvidó la mochila?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:36
translate spanish jezp1_fb6477e7:

    # det "Yes! But it gets even better."
    det "¡Sí! Pero aún hay más."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:38
translate spanish jezp1_1b990547:

    # det "While we were kind of chuckling about how dumb this guy is, there's a knock on the door."
    det "Mientras nos reíamos un poco de lo tonto que es este tipo, llamaron a la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:39
translate spanish jezp1_642a380b:

    # det "I answer and it's that same guy who's on the school ID!"
    det "Abrí y era el mismo chico que aparecía en el carné universitario."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:40
translate spanish jezp1_959deb45:

    # pc "Oh no."
    pc "Oh, no."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:42
translate spanish jezp1_928249b1:

    # det "He just looks at me and asks \"Can I have my bag, please?\""
    det "Se limitó a mirarme y me preguntó: «¿Me devuelves mi mochila, por favor?»."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:43
translate spanish jezp1_a9626bec:

    # det "I could barely read him his rights while I was laughing so hard."
    det "Apenas pude leerle sus derechos de lo mucho que me reía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:44
translate spanish jezp1_7417188d:

    # pc "That's insane. How stupid."
    pc "Es una locura. Qué estupidez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:46
translate spanish jezp1_b555e5c0:

    # det "I like cases like that. Bad guy goes to jail and nobody gets hurt."
    det "Me gustan los casos así. El malo va a la cárcel y nadie sale herido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezp1.rpy:47
translate spanish jezp1_4d597743:

    # det "I wish they could all go that way."
    det "Ojalá todos pudieran acabar así."

